    &lt;dd&gt; (Release 2015-04-24)&lt;/dd&gt;
    &lt;dd&gt;Prime Video&lt;/dd&gt;
    &lt;dd&gt;B00WAMAKZQ (ASIN)&lt;/dd&gt;
